{"tid":2045413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"簡單駁斥崔天凱於Bloomberg評論欄文章中解釋中央訂立港版國安法的理由（歡迎轉發）","createTime":"2020-05-31T20:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T20:07:14.000Z","uid":294955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b690812d9cec9d88650eb0336cdd556bb95fb1a6","tid":2045413,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T20:07:14.000Z","msg":"中國駐美大使崔天凱五月三十日在Bloomberg評論版撰文解釋中央在港版國安法立場時，指國安法將會「保護奉公守法的公民」(protect law-abiding citizens)。<br />\n<br />\n其實不久之前的李文亮事件已表明大陸官方的「奉公守法」觀念容不下一些講真話報真相的良心行為，只要官方認為該行為「危害國家安全」（jeopardize national security），你就不再是「奉公守法的公民」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-05-30/china-s-u-s-ambassador-on-hong-kong-national-security-law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2020-05-30%2Fchina-s-u-s-ambassador-on-hong-kong-national-security-law&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=91bd5c5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-05-30/china-s-u-s-ambassador-on-hong-kong-national-security-law</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kS8kLRn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkS8kLRn.png&h=23153e6c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}